title: Your notes will go here! Click to view the full note.
text:
This is where the full note will be displayed! Thanks for clicking. 
To delete this note, press the trash icon to the right of this note in the note list. 
To write a new note, press the pencil icon in the top right of the page. Once you have a new note written, press the save icon to add it to your notes list! 
Happy note taking!
